{"type": "article", "id": 35180, "title": "给手工控准备礼物？这里有一份推荐｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-12-02T23:36:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 660, "name": "手工"}, {"id": 5504, "name": "礼物"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 489, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016120222250037AKiLeuOvxoVs1d.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">不知不觉间，又到了年末到新年初的节日季。如果你身边有个热爱手工小玩意儿的朋友，本周的这份礼物指南就是特意为你准备的。</p><h2>Yarn Bowl by Barruntando</h2><p>有小动物为你“看守”毛线，连编织都变得甜蜜起来。来自西班牙的 <a href=\"http://www.barruntando.etsy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Barruntando</a> 是一个手工陶器品牌，旗下的毛线碗除了一些基本造型之外，还有设计成诸如狐狸、刺猬以及蝙蝠（这可是万圣节特别版）的款式。它们的配色都非常清新，既时尚又实用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/es/shop/Barruntando?section_id=15068368&amp;ref=shopsection_leftnav_2\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买这些可爱的毛线碗，售价为 33.55 至 37.02 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215005N3R1aQYuKtWjBlqs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671928\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612022150055bjQ7hrl8nDKXBwE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671928\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215006UsjrkqZHt5EMWlvO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671928\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215005wYk0ZBljDtxmOgoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671928\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cat bed by Agnes Felt</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/AgnesFelt\" rel=\"nofollow\">Agnes Felt</a> 是一个来自立陶宛的品牌，专门经营手工制成的羊毛毡制品。旗下的猫窝都围绕着猫咪为主题打造，比如顶部凸起的“猫耳”、猫脸造型的入口，甚至还有连树叶和枝梢上的鸟窝都如实还原的树型猫窝，看起来都非常可爱。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/AgnesFelt/items?section_id=13169506\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>订购，售价从 99 美元到 390 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612022152208LKmYQj7fn6gVp2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.871930\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215220OTWcMPC2gvs71ed9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.819298\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215221bGFrILciwUxTgEXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.194737\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215222631oML7qdfKb2sG9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Matchbox Card by Shop3xu</h3><p>想用更有创意的方式告白或是送去祝福的话，不妨试试这些由越南工作室 <a href=\"http://www.shop3xu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shop3xu</a> 手工制作的火柴盒。和纸质贺卡不同的是，拉出盒子的动作让那些充满趣味的暖心祝福多了一种惊喜感。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/3xudesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店链接</a>，你还可以在它的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shop3xu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 上看到更多实物图。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215335gsWA0u1nKmRztOkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215335LG0QY1eFKqNBSWya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215335BUN3gkPSK7RwpMxz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612022153369zvCV8iOQyTjYa0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Book Clutch Bag by MrsChaplinShop</h3><p>莫斯科 <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/MrsChaplinShop\" rel=\"nofollow\">MrsChaplinShop</a> 出品的手拿包都以真实的实体书作为参照，帆布外壳上那些精美的图案都由设计师 Tatiana 亲手用羊毛编织而成。除了以《小王子》、《百年孤独》和《简·爱》等经典著作为主题的款式之外，Tatiana 还允许顾客进行私人定制。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/MrsChaplinShop/items?section_id=15345030\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些吸睛的手拿包，售价从 380 到 590 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215527iFvHofNP8EzDu4lO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215527E0Y4MzfB7rxhiwpC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215527gAtUJ4ZE8OiuYDfK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612022155281XLh0WMpbVDHzr2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mosevic by Jack Spencer &amp; Alex Boswell</h3><p>拥有可持续产品设计教育背景的 Jack Spencer 和 Alex Boswell 在创立 Mosevic 前花费了四年来开发新型的固体丹宁制品，最后他们利用回收来的牛仔裤制成了丹宁风的太阳眼镜框：在 Mosevic 去年建立的 Kickstarter 众筹页面上，他们用“丹宁新篇章”来形容这个让人眼前一亮的创意。剪下的布料堆叠后会通过树脂融合，制成一块块模版后再进行切割、打磨，最终变成了漂亮的镜框。由于每一条裤子都各不相同并且全部采用手工制作，每一副太阳眼镜也都独一无二。目前，Mosevic 旗下共有 Signature Denim、Worn 和 Vicunha 三个系列，这是它的<a href=\"http://mosevic.com/collections/all\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格从 129 到 169 英镑不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215632wNRfXEpJGLSkj28l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215632ODgGrXfhYQv9K2sx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215632QtnZsmBPdX6Shk5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215633kHtuaXS037JKsTAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coaster set by CRESUS artisanat</h3><p>居住在美国洛杉矶的织物爱好者 Angie Cho 在 Esty 上经营着一家名为 Yumster Friends 的网店，出售她亲手编织的羊毛玩具和小篮子。除了猫咪、熊和兔子这些可爱的动物之外，你还能找到她为了纪念 David Bowie <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/248492784/david-bowie-cat-plush\" rel=\"nofollow\">特别设计的款式</a>。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/YumsterFriends\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些小巧精美的手工织物，售价从 24 到 44 美元不等。如果你对她的设计感兴趣的话，还可以在她的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yumsterfriends/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 上看到更多照片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215733xjdSRDQ0YB7va5P6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215733YoeCT4s1yiS5uvFq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215733wnz7yPj2Ksgd4puB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202215733xlQtwaVS8DAYp52b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}